headline.print_headline: East and West, Ukraine Rival Camps Dig In
headline.main: East and West, Ukraine Rival Camps Dig In

lead_paragraph: If armies march on their stomachs, then Ukraine's rival protest camps could be in for a long campaign, judging by the cooks hard at work behind the barricades in Kiev and Donetsk on Friday.
